track_notes: Nice hike along the Appalachian Trail from Carvers Gap.  Plenty of parking at the gap
Easy hike on the AT to Roan High Knob from the Cloudland parking lot. If the gated road at Carvers Gap is open, this is by far the easiest access route to Roan High Knob.
track_title: W4T/SU-005 - Roan High Knob from Cloudland
